The Sporting Chef's Better Venison Cookbook (EPUB)


Scott Leysath
Year: 2012 
ISBN: 1440234574 
Language: English 
176 Pages 
Format: EPUB 
Size:3.75 MB

Scott Leysath has a mission: to give you venison recipes you'll use again and again. Nothing makes him happier than a cookbook full of food stains and hand-written notes. This book features 100 of his favorites, from appetizers, salads, soups and stews, stovetop dishes, great grilled venison and more. If you long for better-tasting venison, you're in for a treat.
